William Converse-Roberts https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_Converse-Roberts 0 William Converse-Roberts is an American actor. He was born in Needham, Massachusetts. He attended both Stony Brook University and the Yale School of Drama. In 1989, he won an Obie Award for his performance in an Off-Broadway production of Love's Labour's Lost. He resides in Los Angeles. William_Converse-Roberts is an_American_actor . He was_born in Needham , Massachusetts . He attended both Stony_Brook_University and the_Yale_School of Drama .
